text: May Irene Olsen (born 22 May 1956) is a Norwegian sport shooter, born in Lørenskog. She competed in women's 10 metre air rifle and 50 metre rifle three positions at the 1988 Summer Olympics in Seoul. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:People from Lørenskog Category:Norwegian female sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Norway Category:Shooters at the 1988 Summer Olympics
